Package: beakr
Type: Package
Title: A Minimalist Webframework for R
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hans", "Martin", email="hans@mazamascience.com", role=c("aut","cre")),
    person("Jonathan", "Callahan", email="jonathan.s.callahan@gmail.com", role=c("aut"))
    )
Author: Hans Martin [aut, cre],
    Jonathan Callahan [aut]
Maintainer: Hans Martin <hans@mazamascience.com>
Description: A minimalist web framework for developing APIs in R that 
    provides a flexible framework for handling common HTTP-requests, errors, 
    logging, and an ability to integrate any R code as server middleware.
